                <h1>About us</h1>
                <p style="color: #070A52; font-size: 0.9rem;">We understand that sexual harassment is a serious issue that can have a significant impact on individuals' lives. Our website is dedicated to providing a safe and confidential platform for individuals to lodge complaints against sexual harassment.</p>
                <br>
                <p style="color: #070A52; font-size: 0.9rem">We are here to listen and support you throughout the process of lodging a complaint. We understand that speaking out against sexual harassment can be challenging, and we strive to create a safe and non-judgmental environment where you can share your experiences and seek assistance.</p>
                <br>
                <p style="color: #070A52; font-size: 0.9rem">Our mission is to raise awareness about sexual harassment, provide a platform for individuals to share their stories, and advocate for change. We believe that by bringing attention to the issue and holding perpetrators accountable, we can work towards creating a safer and more inclusive society for all.</p>
                <br>
